---
// DailyToll.astro - Real-time impact dashboard
import DailyTollMetrics from './DailyTollMetrics.astro';
import unforkData from '../data/unfork-nepal-data.json';
---

<section id="daily-toll" class="daily-toll-section">
  <div class="daily-toll-container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2 class="section-title">The Daily Toll of Corruption</h2>
    </div>


    <div class="toll-context">
      <div class="context-cards">
        <div class="context-card emotional-card">
          <div class="context-icon">üè•</div>
          <h3>Medical Emergencies</h3>
          <p>People die every day because they can't reach hospitals due to missing roads and infrastructure.</p>
          <div class="emotional-testimonial">
            <em>"My daughter bled to death on the way to the hospital. The road was just a promise."</em>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="context-card emotional-card">
          <div class="context-icon">üè´</div>
          <h3>Education Crisis</h3>
          <p>We lose doctors who save lives, engineers who build bridgess, artists who ease pain, teachers who educate the next generation, and leaders who fight corruption.</p>
          <div class="emotional-testimonial">
            <em>"My son dreams of being a doctor, but studies under a tree. Where did the school money go?"</em>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="context-card emotional-card">
          <div class="context-icon">üë®‚Äçüë©‚Äçüëß‚Äçüë¶</div>
          <h3>Family Breakdown</h3>
          <p>Families lose homes and livelihoods when development funds disappear into corrupt pockets.</p>
          <div class="emotional-testimonial">
            <em>"We lost everything to corruption. Now my children go hungry while thieves get rich."</em>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="context-card emotional-card">
          <div class="context-icon">üí∞</div>
          <h3>Wasted Resources</h3>
          <p>Billions meant for public welfare are siphoned off, leaving communities in perpetual poverty.</p>
          <div class="emotional-testimonial">
            <em>"Our village waited 10 years for electricity. The money came and went, but darkness remains."</em>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="toll-dashboard">
      <div class="data-sources-notice">
        <p class="sources-text">
          Data verified by: {unforkData.dataSources.map(source => source.organization).join(', ')}
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="toll-cta">
      <div class="cta-content">
        <h3>This Doesn't Have to Continue</h3>
        <p>Your action today can stop tomorrow's tragedy. Join us in exposing and ending corruption.</p>
        <div class="cta-buttons">
          <a href="#case-studies" class="cta-button primary">
            See Real Cases
          </a>
          <a href="https://forms.gle/3mknr3AVW7UWvNnLA" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="cta-button secondary">
            Become a Volunteer
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .daily-toll-section {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(139, 0, 0, 0.95) 0%, rgba(220, 20, 60, 0.9) 100%);
    padding: 5rem 0;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .daily-toll-section::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1559027615-cd4628902d4a?w=1920&h=1080&fit=crop&crop=center') center/cover;
    opacity: 0.1;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .daily-toll-container {
    max-width: 1400px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    color: white;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    text-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }

  .section-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    opacity: 0.9;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .toll-dashboard {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .toll-metrics-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .data-sources-notice {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .sources-text {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin: 0;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .sources-link {
    color: #FFD700;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border: 1px solid #FFD700;
    border-radius: 20px;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .sources-link:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.1);
    color: white;
  }

  .toll-context {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .context-cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .context-card {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .context-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
  }

  .context-icon {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .context-card h3 {
    color: white;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .context-card p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .emotional-testimonial {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    border-left: 3px solid #FFD700;
  }

  .emotional-testimonial em {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    display: block;
    position: relative;
  }

  .emotional-testimonial em::before {
    content: '"';
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: #FFD700;
    position: absolute;
    top: -5px;
    left: -10px;
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  .toll-cta {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: 0 16px 48px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  }

  .cta-content h3 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: #DC143C;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .cta-content p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #333;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    max-width: 500px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .cta-button {
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    display: inline-block;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  }

  .cta-button.primary {
    background: #DC143C;
    color: white;
    border: 2px solid #DC143C;
  }

  .cta-button.primary:hover {
    background: #B01030;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(220, 20, 60, 0.4);
  }

  .cta-button.secondary {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    color: #DC143C;
    border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 1);
  }

  .cta-button.secondary:hover {
    background: white;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .section-title {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    .section-subtitle {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .toll-metrics-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .context-cards {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .context-card {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }

    .cta-content h3 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .cta-buttons {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .cta-button {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 300px;
    }
  }
</style>
